#

Crispy Buttermilk Fried Chicken with Sweet Potato Mash and Garlic Green Beans

$15.99
950 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

dairygluten

Dietary Tags:

high-proteincomfort foodgluten-free

Tags:

fried chickensoul foodAmerican cuisine

Description

Juicy buttermilk fried chicken with a crispy coating, paired with creamy sweet potato mash and sautéed green beans infused with garlic flavor.

Ingredients

  • chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • buttermilk: 2 cups
  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • paprika: 2 tsp
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • onion powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • butter: 4 tbsp
  • green beans: 2 cups
  • garlic cloves: 3, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
